With ongoing gym construction at Palo Alto High School, the 2016 Winter Rally featured a staff-vs.-student soccer game. The staff beat the seniors, 3-2, and the Associated Student Body announced the Prom 2016 location to be the Design Galleria in San Francisco. Watch the highlights of the game.

https://youtu.be/QhNuIAZT9xg

